channel.name: discord-announcements
channel.topic: This channel is used for discord announcements such as rule changes, tweaks to the server and whatnot - Anything related to this server!

messages.content: Hello all! We have made a small change to the server rules. To ensure everyone can participate in the best way possible, English will now be the primary language for this server. Please only use English for communications in channels. If you would like to revisit the server rules head over to #rules. Thanks!
We're experiencing some technical difficulties in #deleted-channel it seems. We're aware of it but waiting on information from Discord about this problem. Sorry for the inconvenience!
And we're back, that was quick \0/

Hello everyone! 

We just added #real-world-aviation & #off-topic, and with that made a slight adjustment to the channel description of #deleted-channel to align with the new channels. Enjoy! 🙂

Hey all! We just added a new reaction role to #self-role - @🔔 WIP. Go ahead and give yourself this role if you'd like to be tagged whenever we post a new Discord-exclusive work-in-progress shot in #wip.

Hey Everyone, 

I’m getting a few messages from IFATC Controllers that they are not getting the role when they become members. This is an automatic process, so sometimes it may not work. 

If you do not receive the role, I’d wait 24 hours just to ensure it wasn’t delayed. If you still do not have the role, please message in the #Missing Roles thread. A Discord or Infinite Flight Moderator will refresh them for you.

Hello @everyone 

We've decided to change things up a bit regarding the channels. 

As you've probably noticed, #deleted-channel has been deleted. We're doing this as 99% of the conversation going on in here, should be happening in #off-topic. 
To discuss Infinite Flight related topics, a new channel called #infiniteflight-discussion has been made. 

So, let's all try to keep the discussions in the correct channel moving forward 🙂 

Thank you!

Happy Weekend!

We have recently begun accepting applications for Airport Editing. This is an open application and will not close. If you are interested, please consider applying. This will allow you the opportunity to edit airports in the very near future as well as help us collect some data on how many folks are actually interested in airport editing, and what type of airports people are most interested in. 

*- No prior editing experience necessary*
*- IFC account required*

🛠️  🪚  🧰

Thanks!

https://community.infiniteflight.com/t/infinite-flight-airport-editing-application/694403

Hello everyone! You may have noticed that the #group-flights category has slightly changed

The original thread channel has now been changed into a forum channel. It’s clean, easy to use and looks super cool 😎 Feel free to check it out!

Before creating a post, please read over the #deleted-channel 

Enjoy! ✈️

@everyone 

**E175 Biz Jet Livery - Community Competition**

The E175 is making great progress and our 3D artists are currently working hard on creating the liveries that you love! As a part of the process, we thought it would be a great idea to get everyone in on the action and host a biz jet livery competition. We're now giving you the opportunity to create your own livery and you'll even be able to have your very own custom registration on it! However, this livery must be a tasteful and original private jet livery creation following the competitor guidelines below:

- Must be a current Infinite Flight Pro subscriber
- Must be a member of the Infinite Flight Discord Server
- Business/private jet inspired livery submission must only be on/for the E175
- Livery must be original and may be created digitally or by hand
- Livery must be clearly presented with multiple angles in a way that can be replicated by artists

**Competition Start:** Wednesday, August 31st
**Competition Deadline:** Wednesday, September 7th
**Winner Announcement:** September 2022

To get involved, read through the form below and submit your design when you're ready. We wish you the very best of luck! 3, 2, 1... Get designing! 🖌️ 

Submission form: https://forms.gle/GMHYFYJvXtQapiL28

*Note: we will internally narrow down the entries and choose a winner. The submission link shouldn’t be shared outside of discord since non-members don’t qualify. Submissions that do not comply with the guidelines will be automatically dismissed. Infinite Flight reserves the right to not select a winning design to preserve the integrity of the fleet design. *

Hi everyone! We have just added the #important-info channel with external links to redirect you to places such as the user guide, forum, video tutorials and more. Hope this helps! Pretty much a quick reference channel ⚡

We're down to the final hours of our Discord livery competition. Finish your creation and submit your E175 business jet livery design! 🎨 

The submission form will close on Wednesday, September 7th. We've loved seeing your creative ideas and can't wait to select one lucky member's livery to join the E175 lineup! 

**Submission Form:** https://forms.gle/GMHYFYJvXtQapiL28

_For rules and details, check out the announcement above_

@everyone  We've concluded our E175 livery design competition and are delighted to announce the *one* lucky winner who's biz jet inspired livery will join the fleet! 

🥁  **And the winner is....** 🥁 

@Samirrrrrr / MxP

MxP wowed us with a clean, distinct, and meaningful livery that would be striking in the skies over any region of the world. This livery will be named `Private (Tulip)` in-app and will display MxP’s chosen aircraft registration, `PH-MUC`.

Thank you to everyone who submitted such creative and original designs!

*The E175 is a work in progress with no set release date. Development timelines and final livery renderings are always subject to change.*

EDIT: MxP has decided to change the registration to `PH-MUC` which will be worn on the final rendering. This is to avoid any misunderstanding with the spoken word when combined for those without context. The original registration was a dedication to the Netherlands (PH) and Ukraine (UKR).

Hi everyone, happy Friday!!! We've just added a new #events channel for event announcements! You'll be notified of Flash Flights, Fly-ins/outs, stage events, community events & more. Keep your eyes peeled... We have an event later today 👀
